## ⚠️ Security Advisory: Unofficial Builds & Redistributed Copies

Please be aware that this project may be redistributed, forked, or re-uploaded outside of this official GitHub repository. While open-source collaboration is encouraged, unofficial builds and redistributed versions can pose serious security risks.

Malicious actors may modify the source code or compiled binaries to include malware, spyware, or information-stealing components. These altered versions can appear legitimate but may compromise your system and personal data.

### 🔒 What You Should Do

* Only download or clone the project from this **official repository**.
* Be cautious when using forks, mirrors, or precompiled binaries from unknown sources.
* Review code changes carefully before building or running modified versions.
* Verify commits, tags, or releases when possible.
* Avoid downloading executables shared through third-party sites or direct messages.

We cannot guarantee the safety, integrity, or authenticity of versions distributed outside this repository.

If you encounter suspicious versions of this software, please report them through GitHub Issues.

Stay cautious and prioritize your security.
